description: Vacation brain: Do you have it? In today’s episode, Lisa has tips and tricks on how to navigate the airport terminal, the hotel mini bar, and room service! Plus, the best (and worst) airlines for healthy food, emergency snacks, and the biggest food fakers! [](www.hungry-girl.com)[www.hungry-girl.com](http://hungry-girl.com)
